ng my personal data to respond to my enquiry, send\nnewsletters, and provide email marketing, in accordance with the <a style=\"text-decoration:underline;\" href=\"https:\/\/www.homecaremedicalsupplies.ie\/pages\/privacy-policy\">Privacy Policy<\/a><\/li>\n  <\/ol>\n<\/div>","full_width":false,"remove_margin":false}}},"order":["main","custom_liquid_Aj8CcQ","custom_liquid_GY9NMt","custom_liquid_pcUUiW","rich_text_LPUAjP","custom_liquid_JczhCn","featured_products_section_JpBYLF","testimonials_Rxwz8i","media_with_text_overlay_two_buttons_8ajBpQ","custom_liquid_AiCqqr"]}